<font color="#FF0000">TRUE STORY (MAYBE)</font><br>
<tt>Fri Aug 29 22:11:28 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Silent Warrior:  We can talk... Dad just took the can of Shineola down from the cupboard, scooped up a fresh cow paddie and took James out behind the barn.  It must be that time of the week again... for Toon Sergeant Duke to get his two hour block of instruction on differences.<br>
Crashed the lawn mower on top of the enemy (fifty clicks south of the air strike) slayed all the commies with my P-38.  I'm slightly pissed...had to walk out with both legs broken..Ahh! It wasn't all that bad...last hundred clicks was down hill.  I took two smoke breaks.  Traded a crossbow (made in Tiawan) to a Marine grunt for his M-60.  Smoked a village and ten sampans.  Had to quit..damn gun had more carbon build up than a Chevy exhaust pipe.<br>
Well, back to the attack..Jack.<br><br>
Mustang Two Four
